            <title><![CDATA[Borderlands 4's New Planet Features One Huge Improvement Over Borderlands 3]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/borderlands-4s-new-planet-features-one-huge-improvement-over-borderlands-3/1100-6532862/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
